item.description:
Reference A A Akinshin, V P Golubyatnikov, I V Golubyatnikov “Mathematical and numerical modeling of gene network functioning” (2011) // International Conference “Modern Problems of Mathematics, Informatics and Bioinformatics”, devoted to the 100th anniversary of professor Alexei A. Lyapunov. Novosibirsk. ISBN: 978-5-905569-03-6. Pp. 81.
Abstract We find conditions of existence of stable cycles in some models of gene networks regulated by negative feedbacks and by simple combinations of negative and positive feedbacks. Special algorithms and programs for numerical simulations of these results are elaborated as well.
